</tbody>
</table>
<p>The total portfolio size is 3 UK mortgaged Buy to Let properties (including any Consent to Let (CTL) properties) per applicant (either solely or jointly) across all lenders, including Bank of Ireland Group. Properties that are owned in the name of a limited company which an applicant is a director of, and applications in progress, should also be included.</p>
<p>Total group exposure is £2,000,000.</p>
<p>*Please note minimum loan size for all Bespoke applications is £150,000, and maximum LTV is 75% including any fees.</p>]]></Value>
